---
title: 'What If the Real Coffee Shortage Is Choice, Not Price?'
date: '2026-04-08'
description: "This week's coffee-market data suggests roasters should watch supplier depth and access spread before they watch the next headline price move."
tags: ['coffee', 'market-intelligence', 'pricing', 'supply-chain']
